                            <comment id="480960" author="tappro" created="Wed, 10 Dec 2025 16:34:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Target doesn&apos;t notify MGS on reconnect about own NIDs so after MGS failover IR is not valid source of information about target NIDs anymore.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Possible solution is to register obd_upcall in MGC, so it will be called on import events and call in turn tgt_nid_notify() with list of local node NIDs again, populating NID tables on MGS&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
